  "body": "# Problem\nIn case of accounts with high value (e.g. a watch-only account kept on cold storage), the value exceeds the card width and pushes the share icon out of view\n\n![Screenshot!UNITO-UNDERSCORE!20200716-225553!UNITO-UNDERSCORE!!UNITO-UNDERSCORE!01](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/87762447-73be3300-c813-11ea-94c7-1b9dc6bd451b.jpg)\n\nA list layout is better suited to accommodate accounts of different values.\n\n![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/87762303-35287880-c813-11ea-9133-c4bc4cc72b32.png)\n\nDesign on [Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/XUehMnhyD1FGcWzvGz6SXqvh/Wallet?node-id=9777%3A37903)\n\n* [ ] Address is displayed in Inter Status\n* [ ] `...` calls bottom sheet with option to `Send` > `Request` > `Share`\n* [ ] `Request` calls tx request flow. This is currently not the case\n* [ ] adapt design for Keycard accounts; design TBD\n\n## Implementation\n## Acceptance Criteria\n## Notes\n## Future Steps",
